  <brief_title>A Pilot Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Effects of Acupuncture in Patients on Prolonged Mechanical Ventilation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Prospective Randomized Study to Evaluate the Effects of Acupuncture in Patients on Prolonged Mechanical Ventilation</official_title>
